name: "The Fields of Grey Complete Set Redeemable Ticket"
description:
"The Fields of Grey Complete Set Redeemable Ticket" may be burned and redeemed for "The Fields of Grey Complete Set" on or before April 29, 2022. There are 10 Redeemable Tickets for 10 Complete Sets. After April 29, 2022 any of the 10 remaining "The Fields of Grey Complete Sets" that were not redeemed will be burned.

"Fields of Grey Complete Set" is a collage NFT that includes all 26 photos, poem, and titles in chronological order
